data.description: This charming duplex promises a combination of comfort, convenience, and potential income generation. It's nestled in a peaceful neighborhood with easy access to Fort Cavazos, schools, and dining options. One side of the duplex is currently tenant-occupied, making this an attractive investment choice. This property boasts two separate units, each featuring 2 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms, and an attached garage. Each unit is thoughtfully designed with open layouts and generously sized living areas. Brand new AC units have been installed in both units this year. The backyards are fully enclosed by a privacy fence, and provide opportunities for outdoor activities and gatherings. Whether you choose to rent both units or live in one while generating rental income from the other, this duplex presents a variety of possibilities. Contact us today to schedule a viewing!
